                     <interp inst="t17980214-47-person436" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am a pawn-broker; I produce the sheet, it was pawned with me, on the 13th of April, by a woman, who called herself Mary Upton, I gave the woman a duplicate.</p>
